{"lemma":"عامِلِي","slug":"عامِلِي","root":"ع.م.ل","root_slug":"ع-م-ل","root_link":"/words/roots/ع-م-ل","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"عامِل","root":"عمل","pos":"N","occurrence_count":12},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":4,"pos_tags":["adj","noun","verb"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":14},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n30588"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B9%D8%A7%D9%85%D9%90%D9%84%D9%90%D9%8A"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to do business with","tags":["transitive"]},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to act in common with"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to treat (in such and such a way)","tags":["transitive"],"examples":[{"text":"عَامِلِ الْكُلَّ بِإِحْسَانٍ تُحَبْ / فَقَدِيمًا جَمَّلَ الْمَرْءَ الْأَدَبْ","english":"Miscellany"}]},{"pos":"adj","gloss":"active, effective"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"factor, constituent, element, causative agent"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"factor (e.g. 6 is a factor of 24)","examples":[{"text":"اَلْعَامِل الْمُشْتَرَك الْأَكْبَر","english":"The highest common factor"}]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"motive power"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"a word that governs the grammatical state of one or more words"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"worker, workman, laborer"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"wage earner, employee"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"maker, producer, manufacturer"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"perpetrator, doer, author"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"governor, lieutenant, vicegerent"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"administrative officer, prefect, district president"}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"Compare عَمِلَ (ʕamila, “to do, to work”).\n\nDerived from the active participle of عَمِلَ (ʕamila, “to do, to act, to work”)."},"ipa":["/ʕaː.ma.la/","/ʕaː.mil/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n30588","headword_ar":"عَامِلٌ","root":"Eml","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Working; labouring; serving,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"doing service: doing, acting,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"performing:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"doing, making, working, manufacturing,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"constructing,"},{"kind":"text","text":"a thing:] act. part. n. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eamila","text_ar":"عَمِلَ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (T, Msb, TA:) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EaAmiluwna","text_ar":"عَامِلُونَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb, K, TA) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eum~aAlN","text_ar":"عُمَّالٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EamalapN","text_ar":"عَمَلَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K, TA,) which last signifies [particularly]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"workers with their hands,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fEl","text_ar":"فعل"},{"kind":"text","text":", K, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in various sorts of work,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in clay"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh, TA) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"building"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"digging"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh, TA)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"&c.;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA;) like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faEalapN","text_ar":"فَعَلَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[a pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faAEilN","text_ar":"فَاعِلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (Mgh:) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EawaAmilu","text_ar":"عَوَامِلُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K, TA,) as pl. of [the fem.]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EaAmilapN","text_ar":"عَامِلَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TA,) [and likewise in this case of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EaAmilN","text_ar":"عَامِلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":",] signifies oxen"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that plough,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that tread the corn,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA,) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"upon which water is drawn,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that are employed in other labours;"},{"kind":"text","text":"and in like manner applied to camels: and it is said in a trad. that in the case of such animals no poorrate is required. (TA.) ―         -b2-  Also ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"An administrator of public affairs;"},{"kind":"text","text":"and particularly"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a governor of a province;"},{"kind":"text","text":"and]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a collector of the poor-rates"},{"kind":"text","text":"[and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the like"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"an agent who manages the affairs and property of another."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.)       -A2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EaAmilu Alr~umoHi","text_ar":"عَامِلُ الرُّمْحِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O, K) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EaAmilatuhu","text_ar":"عَامِلَتُهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The part, of the spear, that is next to the head, exclusive of the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"vaEolab","text_ar":"ثَعْلَب"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"portion that enters into the head"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (S, O:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Sador","text_ar":"صَدْر"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"fore part"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the spear,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"exclusive of the head,"},{"kind":"text","text":"accord. to A'Obeyd"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"two cubits in length:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) or, as some say,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the spear-head itself"},{"kind":"text","text":"is called"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EaAmilN","text_ar":"عَامِلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (O, TA:) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EawaAmilu","text_ar":"عَوَامِلُ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*iraAEN","text_ar":"ذِرَاعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", last sentence."}],"source_refs":["T","Msb","TA","K","Mgh","S","O"]}]},"classical_definitions":{"source":"hawramani","url":"https://arabiclexicon.hawramani.com/%D8%B9%D8%A7%D9%85%D9%84/","headword_ar":"عامل","entries":[{"lexicon_id":"dictionary_18","lexicon_en":"Al-Sharīf al-Jurjānī, Kitāb al-Taʿrīfāt (d. 1413 CE)","lexicon_ar":"كتاب التعريفات للشريف الجرجاني","permalink":"https://arabiclexicon.hawramani.com/?p=23401#0f7f95","body_html":"<span>ما أضمر عامله على شريطة التفسير: هو كل اسم بعده فعل أو شبهة، مشتغل عنه بضمير أو متعلقه لو سلط عليه هو أو ما ناسبه لنصبه، مثل: زيدا ضربته.</span>"},{"lexicon_id":"dictionary_18","lexicon_en":"Al-Sharīf al-Jurjānī, Kitāb al-Taʿrīfāt (d. 1413 CE)","lexicon_ar":"كتاب التعريفات للشريف الجرجاني","permalink":"https://arabiclexicon.hawramani.com/?p=23401#36d713","body_html":"<span>العامل: ما أوجب كون آخر الكلمة على وجه مخصوص من الإعراب.<br></span><br>العامل القياسي: هو ما صح أن يقال فيه: كل ما كان كذا فإنه يعمل كذا، كقولنا: غلام زيد، لما رأيت أثر الأول في الثاني وعرفت علته قست عليه: ضرب زيد، وثوب بكر.<br><br>العامل السماعي: هو ما صح أن يقال فيه: هذا يعمل كذا وهذا يعمل كذا، وليس لك أن تتجاوز، كقولنا: إن \"الباء\" تجر، و\"لم\" تجزم، وغيرهما.<br><br><div>العامل المعنوي: هو الذي لا يكون للسان فيه حظ، وإنما هو معنى يعرف بالقلب.</div>"}]}}